To enable the numbered page navigation style, open your `pages.php` file then find the code that looks like one of the examples below:

~~~ .html
<nav><?php echo $page->pager; ?></nav>
~~~

~~~ .php
<?php static::pager(); ?>
~~~

Replace with this:

~~~ .php
<?php static::pager('step'); ?>
~~~

